Is 91 a prime number?

A:

You can use the following code:
public static boolean isPrime(int n) {
    if (n <= 1) {
        return false;
    }
    for (int i = 2; i < n; i++) {
        if (n % i == 0) {
            return false;
        }
    }
    return true;
}

